title: Helping Bronze players improve, EP 6.

embed.description: This is part of a series, where I try and help others go from Bronze to silver. Heck maybe even gold. Im not the one playing, Im spectating a game. If you are bronze and want some help, let me know.

body:
Its this guys second attempt at darius top.
Also, have you guys tried out the new Q?
Its pretty fun, im recording my provisional series. So they will be out soon.

replies.body: Hey man, another great tutoring vid, do you think you could do one for me? XD

Ok, sorry it took so long.
I was moving to a new house and didn't have internet connection.

I can if you wish. I tend to yell a lot, but I never go "OMFG your bad, go die"
Its usually I get salty and upset XD then explain what I think should have happened.

I can add you later, spectate three ranked games when I have some time.
